(3)

REFERENCES TO NIKE BRAND WHOLESALE EQUIVALENT REVENUES ARE INTENDED TO PROVIDE CONTEXT AS TO THE OVERALL CURRENT NIKE BRAND MARKET FOOTPRINT ON A WHOLESALE REVENUE BASIS. NIKE

BRAND WHOLESALE EQUIVALENT REVENUES CONSIST OF 1) SALES TO EXTERNAL WHOLESALE CUSTOMERS AND 2) INTERNAL SALES FROM OUR WHOLESALE OPERATIONS TO OUR DIRECT TO CONSUMER OPERATIONS AT PRICES THAT ARE COMPARABLE TO PRICES CHARGED TO EXTERNAL WHOLESALE

CUSTOMERS. NIKE BRAND WHOLESALE EQUIVALENT REVENUES DO NOT INCLUDE THE ESTIMATION OF SALES MADE BY NIKE BRAND LICENSEES AS THE AMOUNTS ARE NOT MATERIAL.

(4)

OTHERS INCLUDE ALL OTHER CATEGORIES AND CERTAIN ADJUSTMENTS THAT ARE NOT ALLOCATED AT THE CATEGORY LEVEL.

